Package com.esri.gpt.catalog.harvest.clients Description

Contains implementations of harvest repository clients. Harvest repository client provides unified way to communicate with remote repository. It allows to check live status of the remote repository, and verify document presence on the remote repository.

Supported protocols
  • ArcIMS
  • Catalog Service for Web
  • Web Accessible Folders
  • Open Archives Initiative
  • Z39.50
